ve%20Gowda's%20grandson%20and%20NDA%20candidate%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20sexually%20assaulting%20several%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20this%20morning%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20the%20BJP%20stand%20is%20clear%20on%20the%20issue%20-%20that%20it%20is%20with%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ematrushakti%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(mothers%20or%20women).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP's%20stand%20is%20clear%20that%20we%20stand%20with%20the%20'%3Cem%3Ematrushakti%3C%2Fem%3E'%20of%20the%20country.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20Congress%2C%20whose%20government%20is%20there%3F%20The%20government%20is%20of%20Congress%20Party.%20Why%20they%20have%20not%20taken%20any%20action%20till%20now%3F%20We%20do%20not%20have%20to%20take%20action%20on%20this%20as%20this%20is%20a%20law%20and%20order%20issue%20of%20the%20state%2C%20state%20government%20has%20to%20take%20action%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Minister%20said%20the%20BJP%20favours%20a%20probe%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20serious%2C%20we%20cannot%20tolerate%20it.%20We%20want%20to%20ask%20Congress%20that%20despite%20being%20in%20power%2C%20why%20hasn't%20the%20government%20acted%20yet%3F%20Priyanka%20(Gandhi%20Vadra)%20ji%20should%20ask%20their%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%20had%20earlier%20criticised%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20over%20the%20sex%20scandal%20involving%20the%20JD(S)%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal%2C%20a%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Karnataka's%20Hassan%20constituency%2C%20is%20contesting%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20but%20the%20JD(S)%20has%20sought%20to%20distance%20the%20BJP%20from%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%20against%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Bdoctored%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20police%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20videos%20of%20him%20surfaced%20on%20Sat