EThe%20woman%20alleged%20that%20Prajwal's%20father%20HD%20Revanna%20also%20sexually%20assaulted%20her%20when%20his%20wife%20was%20not%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20filed%20a%20complaint%20claiming%20that%20the%20videos%20being%20circulated%20are%20doctored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2033-year-old%20left%20for%20Germany%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20shortly%20after%20the%20videos%20emerged%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal's%20father%20HD%20Revanna%2C%20who%20is%20also%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20is%20MLA%20from%20Holenarasipur%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHD%20Revanna%20too%20accused%20political%20rivals%20of%20creating%20a%20conspiracy%20out%20of%20%26quot%3Bold%20videos%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20formed%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20to%20look%20into%20the%20obscene%20videos%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20set%20up%20the%20SIT%20came%20after%20the%20state%20women's%20commission%20recommended%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20to%20take%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20reports%20of%20Prajwal%20leaving%20the%20country%20pending%20a%20probe%2C%20Karnataka%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20said%20yesterday%20Prajwal%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20return%20to%20India%20by%20the%20SIT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20State%20Commission%20for%20Women%20chairperson%20Nagalakshmi%20Choudhary%20said%20that%20the%20pen%20drive%20she%20received%20had%20hundreds%20of%20explicit%20videos%2C%20some%20purportedly%20showing%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Hassan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20Leader%20Devaraje%20Gowda%2C%20who%20was%20the%20party's%20Holenarsipura%20candidate%20during%20the%202023%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20has%20also%20claimed%20that%20had%20written%20to%20then%20state%20president%20BY%20Vijayendra%20in%20December%20last%20year%2C%20flagging%20%26quot%3Bgrave%20allegations%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20HD%20Deve%20Gowd