2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fzerodhas-nithin-kamath-makes-first-public-appearance-after-stroke-getting-back-5555072%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fzerodhas-nithin-kamath-makes-first-public-appearance-after-stroke-getting-back-5555072%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netanyahu%2C%20Israeli%20Officials%20Face%20Potential%20Arrest%20Warrants%20By%20World%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20voicing%20concern%20that%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20could%20be%20preparing%20to%20issue%20arrest%20warrants%20for%20government%20officials%20on%20charges%20related%20to%20the%20conduct%20of%20its%20war%20against%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20-%20which%20can%20charge%20individuals%20with%20war%20crimes%2C%20crimes%20against%20humanity%20and%20genocide%20-%20is%20investigating%20Hamas'%20October%207%20cross-border%20attack%20and%20Israel's%20devastating%20military%20assault%20on%20Hamas-ruled%20Gaza%2C%20now%20in%20its%20seventh%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Israeli%20media%20reports%20that%20the%20ICC%20might%20soon%20issue%20arrest%20warrants%20for%20senior%20Israeli%20government%20and%20military%20officials%2C%20Foreign%20Minister%20Israel%20Katz%20on%20Sunday%20warned%20Israeli%20embassies%20to%20bolster%20their%20security%20because%20of%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bwave%20of%20severe%20antisemitism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20the%20court%20(ICC)%20to%20refrain%20from%20issuing%20arrest%20warrants%20against%20senior%20Israeli%20political%20and%20security%20officials%2C%26quot%3B%20Katz%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20bow%20our%20heads%20or%20be%20deterred%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20fight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20any%20ICC%20decisions%20would%20not%20affect%20Israel's%20actions%20but%20would%20set%20a%20dangerous%20precedent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20officials%20are%20worried%20that%20the%20court%20could%20issue%20arrest%20warrants%20against%20Netanyahu%20and%20other%20top%20officials%20for%20alleged%20violations%20of%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Israeli%20media%20have%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20the%20ICC%20is%20also%20considering%20arrest%20warrants%20for%20leaders%20from%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%2C%20based%20in%20The%20Hague%2C%20and%20Hamas%2C%20Gaza's%20ruling%20group%2C%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20not%20a%20member%20of%20the%20court%20and%20does%20not%20recognise%20its%20jurisdiction%2C%20but%20the%20Palestinian%20territories%20were%20admitted%20with%20the%20status%20of%20a%20member%20state%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20ICC%20Chief%20Prosecutor%20Karim%20Khan%20said%20the%20court%20had%20jurisdiction%20over%20any%20potential%20war%20crimes%20committed%20by%20Hamas%20fighters%20in%20Israel%20and%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20has%20said%20his%20team%20is%20actively%20investigating%20any%20crimes%20allegedly%20committed%20in%20Gaza%20and%20that%20those%20who%20are%20in%20breach%20of%20the%20law%20will%20be%20held%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20is%20an%20independent%20organization%20and%20their%20efforts%20are%20being%20undertaken%20without%20any%20contact%20or%20interference%20by%20the%20U.S.%2C%26quot%3B%20U.S.%20Ambassador%20to%20the%20U.N.%20Linda%20Thomas-Greenfield%20told%20reporters%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.S.%20-%20Israel's%20ally%20-%20is%20also%20not%20a%20member%20of%20the%20court.%20A%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20said%20later%20on%20Monday%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20has%20no%20jurisdiction%20in%20this%20situation%2C%20and%20we%20do%20not%20support%20its%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EINTERNATIONAL%20ISOLATION%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Gillet%2C%20a%20lecturer%20in%20international%20law%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Essex%20in%20England%2C%20said%20anyone%20issued%20with%20an%20arrest%20warrant%20would%20be%20unable%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20more%20than%20120%20countries%20that%20are%20members%20of%20the%20ICC%2C%20including%20most%20European%20countries%2C%20Japan%20and%20Australia%2C%20or%20they%20could%20be%20detained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGillet%20said%20if%20arrest%20warrants%20were%20issued%20against%20Israeli%20officials%2C%20some%20allied%20countries%20could%20take%20action%20such%20as%20reducing%20weapons%20transfers%20or%20scaling%20back%20diplomatic%20visits%2C%20increasing%20Israel's%20international%20isolation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20make%20%26quot%3Bit%20more%20difficult%20for%20Western%20liberal%20democracies%20to%20engage%20with%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%2C%20Hamas%20led%20an%20attack%20on%20Israeli%20military%20bases%20and%20communities%20in%20which%201%2C200%20people%20were%20killed%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20and%20253%20were%20taken%20as%20hostages%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20tallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20since%20launched%20a%20ground%2C%20air%20and%20sea%20offensive%20that%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2034%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20according%20to%20Gaza%20authorities%2C%20and%20has%20laid%20much%20of%20the%20small%2C%20densely%20populated%20coastal%20territory%20to%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gaza%20Health%20Ministry%20does%20not%20distinguish%20between%20combatants%20and%20non-combatants%20in%20its%20casualty%20reports%20but%20most%20of%20the%20fatalities%20have%20been%20civilians%2C%20health%20officials%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20says%20that%20it%20takes%20precautions%20to%20minimise%20civilian%20deaths%20and%20that%20at%20least%20a%20third%20of%20the%20Gaza%20fatalities%20are%20combatants%2C%20figures%20that%20Hamas%20has%20dismissed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20campaign%20has%20displaced%20most%20of%20the%20blockaded%20Palestinian%20enclave's%202.3%20million%20people%20and%20created%20a%20humanitarian%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20at%20the%20ICC%20is%20separate%20from%20a%20genocide%20case%20launched%20against%20Israel%20at%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%2C%20also%20based%20in%20The%20Hague.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICJ%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20World%20Court%2C%20is%20a%20United%20Nations%20court%20that%20deals%20with%20disputes%20between%20states%2C%20while%20the%20ICC%20is%20a%20treaty-based%20criminal%20court%20focusing%20on%20individual%20criminal%20responsibility%20for%20war%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714458600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fcv54u4go_benjamin-netanyahu_625x300_30_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-benjamin-netanyahu-israeli-officials-face-potential-arrest-warrants-by-international-criminal-court-5555045%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20is%20voicing%20concern%20that%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20(ICC)%20could%20be%20preparing%20to%20issue%20arrest%20warrants%20for%20government%20officials%2C%20including%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20on%20charges%20related%20to%20its%20war%20against%20Hamas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-benjamin-netanyahu-israeli-officials-face-potential-arrest-warrants-by-international-criminal-court-5555045%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-benjamin-netanyahu-israeli-official