of%20structural%20mismanagement%2C%20has%20to%20import%20its%20energy%20and%20power%20supplies.%20Neighbouring%20Iran%20is%20naturally%20the%20most%20logical%20source%20for%20such%20procurement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPakistan's%20Quandary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20already%20fulfilled%20its%20part%20of%20the%20agreement%20by%20completing%20a%201%2C100%20km%20section%20from%20the%20South%20Pars%20gas%20fields%20to%20the%20Pakistan%20border.%20In%202014%2C%20on%20Pakistan's%20request%2C%20it%20extended%20the%20deadline%20by%20a%20decade.%20That%20is%20set%20to%20end%20in%20September%20this%20year%2C%20and%20Pakistan%20is%20yet%20to%20complete%20its%20part%20of%20the%20pipeline.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fshows%2Findia-global%2Fus-warns-pakistan-over-iran-ties-china-losing-grip-in-indo-pacific-gaza-ceasefire-at-a-standstill-778628%5C%22%3Eglobal%20sanctions%20against%20Iran%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20resultant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-warns-pakistan-of-potential-risk-of-sanctions-over-trade-deal-with-iran-5509300%5C%22%3Egeopolitical%20pressure%20on%20Pakistan%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20the%20main%20reasons%20for%20this%20severe%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20and%20Pakistan%20have%20had%20uneasy%20relations%20for%20years%2C%20strained%20in%20part%20by%20the%20latter's%20close%20ties%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20UAE%2C%20Iran's%20rivals%20in%20the%20region%2C%20as%20also%20by%20Pakistan's%20geopolitical%20and%20economic%20dependence%20on%20the%20US.%20Iran%20has%20frequently%20blamed%20Pakistan%20for%20fomenting%20terrorism%20in%20its%20border%20regions%20of%20Sistan-Baluchistan%20and%20of%20nurturing%20the%20Taliban%20to%20weaken.%20Discrimination%20against%20the%20Shia%20minority%20in%20Pakistan%20has%20added%20to%20the%20friction%20over%20the%20years.%20Nonetheless%2C%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20taken%20care%20to%20strike%20a%20more%20conciliatory%20tone%20towards%20Iran%20given%20Islamabad's%20rivalry%20with%20India%20on%20its%20eastern%20borders.%20For%20instance%2C%20Pakistan's%20refusal%20to%20send%20troops%20to%20Yemen%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Saudi-led%20Sunni%20coalition%20was%20majorly%20due%20to%20this%20factor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Tit-For-Tat%20Strikes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20came%20to%20a%20head%20recently%20after%20the%20tit-for-tat%20strikes%20in%20January%20that%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan%20carried%20out%20against%20each%20other%20to%20preempt%20%26quot%3Bterrorists%26quot%3B.%20Soon%20after%20the%20strikes%2C%20Iranian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Abdolahein%20visited%20Islamabad%20as%20a%20gesture%20of%20reconciliation.%20These%20attacks%20had%20come%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20heightened%20tensions%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-how-6-months-of-israel-hamas-war-has-hit-gaza-5373468%5C%22%3EIsrael-Hamas%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20disruption%20of%20shipping%20lines%20by%20the%20Iran-backed%20Houthi%20militias.%20Tehran's%20fear%20was%20that%20Pakistan's%20territory%20might%20be%20used%20by%20the%20US%20to%20attack%20it%2C%20just%20as%20it%20had%20been%20used%20in%20the%20past%20to%20target%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20during%20the%20Afghan%20jihad%2C%20and%20later%2C%20the%20Taliban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20context%2C%20the%20recent%20Pakistan%20visit%20of%20Iranian%20President%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%20can%20also%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20bid%20to%20smooth%20ruffled%20feathers.%20During%20the%20visit%2C%20both%20sides%20inked%20six%20economic%20agreements%2C%20vowing%20to%20take%20trade%20beyond%20the%20current%20volume%20of%20a%20paltry%20%242%20billion.%20A%20joint%20statement%20issued%20during%20the%20trip%20included%20plans%20for%20cooperation%20in%20the%20energy%20domain%2C%20including%20the%20pipeline%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPenalty%20Blues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20tensions%20with%20Iran%20seem%20allayed%20for%20now%2C%20Pakistan's%20headache%20is%20now%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20to%20move%20ahead%20with%20the%20pipeline%20or%20face%20the%20threat%20of%20penalty.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20Tehran%20has%20issued%20an%20ultimatum%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20finish%20the%20pipeline%20segment%20by%202024%20or%20incur%20financial%20repercussions%20amounting%20to%20nearly%20%2418%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20experienced%20inflation%20rates%20exceeding%2020%25%20on%20a%20year-on-year%20basis.%20According%20to%20the%20Pakistan%20Bureau%20of%20Statistics%2C%20big%20industry%20production%20has%20contracted%20significantly%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20resulting%20in%20high%20levels%20of%20unemployment.%20Domestic%20coal%20and%20gas%20prices%20have%20risen%20considerably%2C%20hitting%20power%20supply.%20Against%20these%20circumstances%2C%20Iran's%20ultimatum%20is%20an%20added%20nightmare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmerican%20Pressure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20this%20year%2C%20the%20caretaker%20government%20in%20Pakistan%20approved%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20pipeline%2C%20which%20would%20comprise%20an%2080%20km%20line%20(of%20a%20total%20of%20780%20km)%20from%20the%20Iranian%20border%20to%20Gwadar.%20However%2C%20the%20US%20responded%20swiftly.%20Last%20month%2C%20Donald%20Lu%2C%20the%20US%20Assistant%20Secretary%20of%20State%20for%20South%20and%20Central%20Asia%20cautioned%20Pakistan%20against%20importing%20gas%20from%20Iran%2C%20warning%20it%20that%20this%20would%20invite%20US%20sanctions.%20While%20the%20Pakistani%20Foreign%20Office%20spokesperson%20has%20said%20this%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Binternal%26quot%3B%20matter%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20Pakistan%20can%20withstand%20US%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20Pakistan's%20largest%20export%20market%3B%20it%20bought%20Pakistani%20goods%20worth%20more%20than%20%245%20billion%20in%202021.%20America%20has%20also%20been%20a%20leading%20investor%20in%20the%20country%20for%20the%20past%2020%20years.%20Last%20year%20in%20August%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20signed%20the%20Communication%20Interoperability%20and%20Security%20Memorandum%20of%20Agreement%2C%20or%20CIS-MOA%2C%20which%20covers%20joint%20exercises%2C%20operations%2C%20training%2C%20basing%20and%20equipment%2C%20as%20well%20as%20sales%20of%20military%20hardware%20to%20Pakistan.%20Last%20year%2C%20%C2%A0it%20was%20the%20US%20that%20helped%20facilitate%20a%20much-needed%20%243%20billion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fimf-approves-disbursal-of-1-1-billion-loan-tranche-to-pakistan-5553115%5C%22%3Ebailout%20loan%20from%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20helped%20Pakistan%20avoid%20a%20default%20on%20its%20international%20payments.%20The%20final%20tranche%20of%20this%20package%20was%20released%20on%20April%2030.%20Pakistan%20is%20also%20looking%20to%20secure%20a%20bigger%20longer-term%20package%20from%20the%20IMF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnother%20Set%20Of%20Complications%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20dimensions%20too.%20Besides%20tensions%20over%20Pakistan's%20nuclear%20programme%20and%20Iran's%20involvement%20in%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20a%20fresh%20irritant%20in%20Iran-US%20relations%20is%20the%20Iranian%20backing%20for%20Russia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20its%20sale%20of%20drones%20to%20Moscow.%20Despite%20the%20debilitating%20energy%20crisis%20Pakistan%20is%20facing%2C%20it%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20Russia's%20heavily%20discounted%20crude%20oil%20precisely%20because%20of%20the%20US%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20now%20is%20whether%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20has%20so%20much%20at%20stake%2C%20is%20in%20a%20position%20to%20risk%20its%20relations%20with%20the%20US%20over%20the%20Peace%20Pipeline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20as%20Pakistan's%20relations%20with%20the%20US%20came%20under%20strain%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%20-%20Afghanistan%20is%20among%20the%20more%20significant%20of%20which%20-%20Islamabad%20turned%20towards%20China%2C%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20UAE%2C%20its%20traditional%20patrons.%20However%2C%20ties%20with%20the%20latter%20two%20have%20also%20frayed%20due%20to%20Yemen.%20While%20there%20has%20been%20some%20damage%20control%2C%20it%20is%20doubtful%20whether%20the%20two%20countries%20will%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20the%20succour%20Pakistan%20may%20need%20in%20case%20it%20goes%20ahead%20with%20the%20pipeline%2C%20and%20consequently%2C%20the%20US%20sanctions%20that%20may%20come%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20China%20Factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20plays%20the%20lead%20role%20in%20the%20Pakistani%20economy%20with%20its%20%2462-billion%20China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20(CPEC).%20However%2C%20running%20through%20Balochistan%20and%20Khyber-Pakhtunkhwa%20Province%2C%20the%20CPEC%20has%20been%20mired%20in%20challenges%20like%20allegations%20of%20opaqueness%20and%20plundering%20of%20local%20resources%2C%20inability%20to%20generate%20local%20employment%2C%20widespread%20local%20resentment%2C%20and%20militant%20attacks.%20Trade-wise%2C%20China%20is%20Pakistan's%20second-largest%20partner%2C%20but%20the%20equation%20is%20heavily%20skewed%20in%20favour%20of%20Beijing.%20Data%20from%202022%20reveals%20that%20while%20China's%20exports%20to%20Pakistan%20stood%20at%20%2421%20billion%2C%20its%20imports%20from%20there%20were%20just%20%242.79%20billion.%20According%20to%20the%20IMF%2C%20Pakistan%20owes%20%246.7%20billion%20in%20commercial%20loans%20to%20China%20and%20is%20thus%20staring%20at%20a%20deep%20debt%20trap.%20Hence%2C%20to%20what%20extent%20China%20would%20be%20able%20to%20help%20Pakistan%20is%20also%20uncertain%2C%20busy%20as%20it%20is%20in%20an%20ever-escalating%20trade%20war%20with%20the%20US%20as%20well%20as%20fighting%20secondary%20sanctions%20for%20its%20own%20trade%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20promised%20to%20help%20Pakistan%20with%20expertise%20and%20know-how%20for%20building%20the%20pipeline.%20Pakistan%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20said%20it%20would%20apply%20for%20a%20sanctions%20waiver%20from%20the%20US.%20With%20the%20latter%20already%20having%20laid%20down%20that%20any%20such%20engagement%20with%20Iran%20would%20invite%20sanctions%2C%20Pakistan%20may%20either%20have%20to%20give%20up%20on%20the%20pipeline%20and%20cough%20up%20a%20watered-down%20penalty%20-%20or%20it%20may%20try%20to%20pivot%20to%20the%20East%20and%20try%20to%20secure%20guarantees%20from%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%20Iran%2C%20and%20its%20Gulf%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20predict%20what%20will%20actually%20happen%2C%20but%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20Pakistan%20is%20in%20an%20unenviable%20position%2C%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Aditi%20Bhaduri%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20political%20analyst)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714458360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ftejjgk64_ibrahim-raisi-meets-pak-pm_625x300_24_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Famid-us-pressure-the-iran-pakistan-pipeline-has-becomes-islamabads-bane-5554811%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20is%20yet%20to%20complete%20its%20part%20of%20the%20pipeline.%20The%20global%20sanctions%20against%20Iran%20and%20the%20resultant%20geopolitical%20pressure%20on%20Islamabad%20from%20the%20Uare%20the%20main%20reasons%20for%20the%20severe%20delay.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.c