mes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20also%20shared%20that%20she%20wasn't%20comfortable%20referring%20to%20herself%20as%20middle-aged%20because%20%26quot%3Bwe%20don't%20know%20if%20this%20is%20middle%20age.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20I%20hesitate%20at%20calling%20things%20'middle%20age'%20simply%20because%20I%20can%20be%20a%20semantic%20stickler%20and%20I%20could%20get%20hit%20by%20a%20car%20later%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Hathaway%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHathaway%20first%20spoke%20about%20quitting%20alcohol%20during%20an%20appearance%20on%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fji12D_aObGw%3Fsi%3DXKGJsPUm7tgyKaxL%26t%3D147%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Ellen%20DeGeneres%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20January%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20quit%20drinking%20back%20in%20October%2C%26quot%3B%20Hathaway%20told%20DeGeneres.%20%26quot%3BFor%2018%20years.%20I'm%20going%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-sober-stopped-drinking-start-family-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estop%20drinking%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20my%20son's%20living%20in%20my%20house%20because%20I%20don't%20totally%20love%20the%20way%20I%20do%20it%20and%20he's%20getting%20to%20the%20age%20where%20he%20really%20needs%20me%20all%20the%20time%20in%20the%20morning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20later%20clarified%20in%20an%20April%202019%20interview%20with%20Modern%20Luxury%20that%20she%20stopped%20drinking%20not%20because%20she%20had%20an%20alcohol%20problem%20but%20because%20she%20had%20really%20bad%20hangovers%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fparents%2Fanne-hathaway-not-drinking-while-son-is-young-hangovers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20last%20hangover%20lasted%20for%20five%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Hathaway%20told%20Modern%20Luxury.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I'm%20at%20a%20stage%20in%20my%20life%20where%20there%20is%20enough%20space%20for%20me%20to%20have%20a%20hangover%2C%20I'll%20start%20drinking%20again%2C%20but%20that%20won't%20be%20until%20my%20kid%20is%20out%20of%20the%20house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHathaway%20has%20two%20sons%2C%20Jonathan%2C%208%2C%20and%20Jack%2C%204%2C%20with%20her%20husband%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanne-hathaway-kids-husband-family-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdam%20Shulman%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20couple%20have%20been%20married%20for%2012%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fhollywood%2Fanne-hathaway-cover-story%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVanity%20Fair%3C%2Fa%3E%20interview%20from%20March%2C%20Hathaway%20also%20spoke%20about%20how%20her%20mental%20health%20has%20improved%20since%20she%20quit%20alcohol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20path%20everybody%20has%20to%20walk%20for%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20Hathaway%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20personal%20experience%20with%20it%20is%20that%20everything%20is%20better.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20was%20wallowing%20fuel.%20And%20I%20don't%20like%20to%20wallow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ajpmonline.org%2Farticle%2FS0749-3797(15)00354-2%2Fabstract%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECDC%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20the%20loss%20in%20productivity%20due%20to%20hangovers%20cost%20the%20economy%20almost%20%2490%20billion%20in%202010%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Fbusiness%2Farchive%2F2015%2F10%2Fthe-cost-of-hangovers%2F411052%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThey%2520found%2520that%2520the%2520most%2520significant%2520cost%2520was%2520the%2520lost%2520productivity%2520of%2520hungover%2520workers%2520who%2520either%2520showed%2520up%2520for%2520work%2520barely%2520able%2520to%2520function%252C%2520or%2520who%2520were%2520unable%2520to%2520show%2520up%2520at%2520all%252C%2520which%2520cost%2520nearly%2520%252490%2520billion.%5C