owerball%20jackpot%20in%20April.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6630613c0dfb1341e9008ee5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECheng%20Saephan%2C%2046%2C%20won%20the%20%241.3%20billion%20Powerball%20jackpot%20in%20April.%3Cp%3EOregon%20Lottery%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20winner%20of%20the%20%241.3%20billion%20Powerball%20jackpot%20in%20Oregon%20is%20a%20Laos-born%20immigrant%20battling%20cancer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe's%20opting%20to%20take%20the%20lump-sum%20option%2C%20and%20will%20receive%20%24422%20million%20after%20taxes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECheng%20Saephan%2C%2046%2C%20plans%20to%20split%20the%20money%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20a%20close%20friend.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20winner%20of%20Oregon's%20%241.3%20billion%20Powerball%20jackpot%20is%20a%2046-year-old%20Laos-born%20immigrant%20who%20opted%20to%20take%20his%20winnings%20in%20a%20lump-sum%20payment%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20he'll%20get%20%24422%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheng%20Saephan%20told%20reporters%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8w-LPLYdguA%26ab_channel%3DKGWNews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20conference%20on%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he's%20been%20battling%20cancer%20for%20eight%20years%20and%20was%20living%20on%20disability%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20winning%20ticket%20was%20one%20of%2020%20bought%20at%20a%20Portland%20convenience%20store%20by%20Saephan%2C%20who%20said%20he%20won%20through%20luck%20and%20his%20religious%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20prayed%20to%20God%20to%20help%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20kids%20are%20young%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20that%20healthy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaephan%20told%20reporters%20that%20after%20praying%2C%20he%20wrote%20out%20all%20the%20numbers%20from%201%20to%2069%20on%20a%20sheet%20of%20paper%20that%20he%20put%20under%20his%20pillow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20slept%20with%20it%20for%20two%20weeks%2C%20and%20then%20I%20win%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaephan%2C%20who's%20been%20an%20Oregon%20resident%20for%2030%20years%20and%20lives%20in%20Portland%2C%20said%20he%20was%20at%20home%20when%20he%20discovered%20he'd%20won%20the%20April%206%20drawing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20initially%20thought%20he'd%20come%20up%20empty%20when%20checking%20his%20bundle%20of%20tickets%20but%20realized%20he%20hit%20the%20jackpot%20when%20looking%20through%20the%20last%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMom%2C%20we're%20rich%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled%20saying%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20who%20was%20drinking%20coffee%20at%20the%20dining%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20intends%20to%20split%20the%20money%20between%20himself%2C%20his%2037-year-old%20wife%2C%20and%20a%20friend%20who%20gave%20him%20%24100%20to%20buy%20the%20batch%20of%20tickets%20that%20led%20to%20the%20jackpot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaephan%20said%20he%20called%20this%20friend%2C%20Laiza%20Chao%2C%20soon%20after%20to%20share%20the%20news.%20Chao%20is%20to%20receive%2025%25%20of%20the%20winnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20said%3A%20'Laiza%2C%20where%20are%20you%3F'%20and%20she%20said%3A%20'I'm%20going%20to%20work%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Saephan.%20%26quot%3BI%20replied%3A%20'You%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20anymore.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaephan%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20aerospace%20industry%20as%20a%20CNC%20operator%20before%20his%20cancer%20diagnosis%2C%20said%20he%20plans%20to%20buy%20his%20%26quot%3Bdream%20home%26quot%3B%20as%20his%20first%20purchase.%20He%20said%20he'd%20spend%20the%20money%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bjust%20normal%26quot%3B%20fashion%20as%20he%20fights%20a%20terminal%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20life%20has%20been%20changed.%20Now%20I%20can%20bless%20my%20family%20and%20hire%20a%20good%20doctor%20for%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Saephan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20continue%20playing%20the%20lottery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20might%20get%20lucky%20again%2C%20I'll%20keep%20playing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20amount%20to%20be%20received%20by%20Saephan%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20and%20Chao%20is%20%24422%2C309%2C193.97%20after%20taxes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oregonlottery.org%2Fpress-releases%2F1-3-billion-powerball-jackpot-winners-announced%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20the%20Oregon%20Lottery.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20lottery%20added%20that%20the%20store%20that%20sold%20the%20winning%20ticket%20is%20getting%20%24100%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaephan's%20Powerball%20win%20is%20the%20state's%20largest%20in%20history.%20Previously%2C%20the%20biggest%20Oregon%20jackpot%20was%20announced%20in%202005%20and%20worth%20%24340%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Oregon%20Lottery%20said%20ticket%20sales%20have%20since%201985%20earned%20some%20%2415.5%20billion%20that%20goes%20toward%20parks%2C%20schools%2C%20veteran%20services%2C%20and%20other%20state%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest-ever%20lottery%20jackpot%20in%20the%20US%20was%20%242.05%20billion%2C%20won%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fedwin-castro-powerball-jackpot-winner-real-estate-buying-spree-california-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEdwin%20Castro%20in%20California%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOregon%20and%20California%20are%20states%20where%20lottery%20winners%20cannot%20remain%20anonymous%20by%20law.%20Only%2017%20US%20states%20allow%20jackpot%20recipients%20to%20hide%20their%20identities%2C%20including%20Texas%2C%20Arizona%2C%20Georgia%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20Maryland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwinner-jackpot-cheng-saephan-cancer-battle-gets-422m-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714449970000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2