5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109711564.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESanchez's%20remarks%20come%20after%20a%20corruption%20complaint%20against%20his%20wife%20Begona%20Gomez%20brought%20by%20Manos%20Limpias%20(Clean%20Hands)%2C%20an%20organization%20with%20a%20connection%20to%20the%20far-right.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fspanish-pm-pedro-sanchez-refuses-to-resign-vows-to-step-up-fight-against-unfounded-attacks%2Farticleshow%2F109711564.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fspanish-pm-pedro-sanchez-refuses-to-resign-vows-to-step-up-fight-against-unfounded-attacks%2Famp_articleshow%2F109711564.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fspanish-pm-pedro-sanchez-refuses-to-resign-vows-to-step-up-fight-against-unfounded-attacks%2Famp_articleshow%2F109711564.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sony%20Launches%20Futuristic%20'Wearable%20Air%20Conditioner'%20Gadget%20To%20Beat%20The%20Heat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESony%20has%20unveiled%20a%20high-tech%20gadget-%20a%20futuristic%20body%20air%20conditioner%20that%20can%20be%20tucked%20into%20the%20back%20of%20your%20shirt.%20This%20innovative%20technology%20offers%20a%20potential%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20hand%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESony's%20%26quot%3Bsmart%20wearable%20thermo%20device%20kit%26quot%3B%20dubbed%20Reon%20Pocket%205%20was%20released%20on%20April%2023.%20The%20device%20is%20a%20wearable%20climate%20control%20system%20that%20promises%20personalized%20comfort%20on%20the%20go.%20Worn%20on%20the%20back%20of%20your%20neck%2C%20this%20innovative%20device%20utilizes%20a%20thermos%20module%20and%20a%20suite%20of%20sensors%20(temperature%2C%20humidity%2C%20and%20motion)%20to%20determine%20your%20ideal%20temperature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Reon%20Pocket%205%20offers%20five%20cooling%20levels%20for%20hot%20days%20and%20four%20warming%20levels%20for%20cooler%20environments%2C%20making%20it%20adaptable%20to%20various%20situations%2C%20from%20crowded%20trains%20to%20chilly%20airplane%20cabins.%20For%20optimal%20performance%2C%20the%20device%20can%20be%20paired%20with%20the%20included%20Reon%20Pocket%20Tag.%20This%20small%2C%20wearable%20tag%20functions%20like%20a%20remote%20sensor%2C%20detecting%20your%20surrounding%20conditions%20and%20sending%20that%20information%20to%20the%20neck%20unit%20for%20proactive%20temperature%20adjustments.%20While%20the%20Reon%20Pocket%205%20works%20independently%2C%20focusing%20solely%20on%20your%20body%20temperature%2C%20the%20tag%20provides%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20personalized%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrefer%20a%20hands-on%20approach%3F%20The%20Reon%20Pocket%205%20can%20be%20controlled%20through%20the%20new%20Reon%20Pocket%20App%2C%20available%20for%20both%20iOS%20and%20Android%20devices.%20This%20app%20allows%20you%20to%20adjust%20the%20five%20cooling%20and%20four%20warming%20levels%20via%20Bluetooth%2C%20making%20it%20perfect%20for%20on-the-go%20adjustments.%20Hikers%2C%20rejoice!%20The%20Reon%20Pocket%205%20boasts%20a%20generous%2017%20hours%20of%20battery%20life%20on%20a%20single%20charge%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techradar.com%2Ftech%2Fsonys-wearable-air-conditioner-is-the-first-step-towards-a-real-dune-stillsuit%5C%22%3ETech%20Radar%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESony's%20innovative%20personal%20climate%20control%20isn't%20entirely%20new.%20The%20Reon%20Pocket%20series%20debuted%20in%20Japan%20back%20in%202019%2C%20with%20later%20versions%20finding%20success%20in%20Asian%20markets%20like%20Hong%20Kong.%20The%20Reon%20Pocket%205%2C%20however%2C%20marks%20a%20global%20expansion%2C%20with%20the%20UK%20market%20receiving%20the%20first%20wave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPre-orders%20for%20the%20Reon%20Pocket%205%20are%20now%20open%20on%20Sony's%20website%2C%20priced%20at%20139%20%C2%A0pounds%20(roughly%20%24170%20USD%20or%20AU%24260).%20%C2%A0These%20pre-orders%20will%20start%20shipping%20on%20May%2015th.%20The%20base%20package%2C%20%26quot%3BReon%205T%2C%26quot%3B%20includes%20the%20device%20itself%2C%20a%20Reon%20Pocket%20Tag%2C%20and%20a%20white%20neckband.%20For%20those%20wanting%20a%20touch%20more%20style%2C%20Sony%20offers%20a%20beige%20neckband%20for%20an%20additional%2025%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESporting%20two%20types%20of%20air%20vent%20covers%2C%20the%20REON%20POCKET%205%20goes%20well%20with%20both%20business%20and%20casual%20styles.%20The%20air%20vent%20for%20business%20style%20extends%20up%20to%20the%20height%20of%20the%20collar%2C%20matching%20the%20shape%20of%20the%20neck%20and%20back%2C%20while%20the%20other%20is%20shorter%20for%20casual%20style%20to%20match%20the%20low%20collar%2C%20both%20of%20which%20allow%20for%20efficient%20airflow%2C%20Sony%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20REON%20POCKET%205%20will%20be%20available%20in%20Singapore%20from%20May%202024%20and%20available%20in%20Malaysia%2C%20Thailand%20and%20Vietnam%20at%20a%20later%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714449600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fh8u32mio_reon-pocket-5_625x300_30_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsony-launches-futuristic-wearable-air-conditioner-gadget-to-beat-the-heat-5554195%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sony's%20smart%20wearable%20thermo%20device%20kit%26quot%3B%20dubbed%20Reon%20Pocket%205%20was%20released%20on%20April%2023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsony-launches-futuristic-wearable-air-conditioner-gadget-to-beat-the-heat-5554195%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-co