ece-lined%20Teckelklub%20Trench%20Coat%20keeps%20dogs%20dry%20and%20warm.%20King%20is%20a%20fan%20of%20this%20coat%2C%20which%20has%20a%20simple%20wraparound%20design%20with%20a%20broad%20collar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jacket%20fastens%20with%20Velcro%20at%20the%20neck%20and%20a%20wide%20strap%20under%20the%20belly.%20While%20that's%20the%20only%20belly%20coverage%20the%20jacket%20provides%2C%20it%20is%20a%20good%20option%20for%20sensitive%20dogs%20because%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20slip%20it%20over%20the%20head%20or%20legs.%20%26quot%3BSome%20jackets%20have%20a%20pullover%20design%20and%20many%20dogs%20are%20not%20comfortable%20putting%20them%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fjeff-chebul-83490b10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJeff%20Chebul%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20professional%20dog%20walker%20and%20owner%20of%20Ranger's%20Squadron%20Dogwalking%20Services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outer%20shell%20is%20100%25%20waterproof%20nylon%2C%20and%203M%20reflective%20piping%20lines%20the%20edges.%20It%20lacks%20a%20hole%20at%20the%20back%20for%20attaching%20a%20leash%20to%20a%20harness%2C%20but%20its%20slim%20fit%20allows%20a%20harness%20to%20be%20worn%20over%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20this%20raincoat%20collected%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20mud%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20wipe%20clean%2C%20and%20after%20machine%20washing%20and%20hanging%20it%20to%20dry%2C%20it%20came%20out%20looking%20brand%20new.%20It%20will%20also%20stand%20up%20to%20a%20low-heat%20cycle%20in%20the%20dryer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20an%20extra%20%2415%2C%20you%20can%20get%20custom%20embroidery%20on%20the%20coat%2C%20including%20a%20monogram%2C%20your%20dog's%20name%2C%20or%20your%20phone%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20dog%20raincoats%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20different%20dog%20rain%20jackets%20are%20drying%20on%20a%20fence.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66301294ec0c696569fef435%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EShoshi%20Parks%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20determine%20the%20best%20dog%20raincoats%2C%20we%20tested%2011%20different%20jackets%20based%20on%20recommendations%20from%20professional%20dog%20walkers.%20The%20jackets%20were%20provided%20as%20review%20samples%20by%20their%20manufacturers%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20the%20Blueberry%20Pet%2C%20Canada%20Pooch%2C%20Pepper%20Pet%2C%20Wildebeest%2C%20and%20Teckelclub%20coats%2C%20which%20Business%20Insider%20purchased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20dry%20weather%20and%20coronavirus%20pandemic%20restrictions%2C%20I%20could%20not%20test%20these%20jackets%20on%20dogs%20of%20multiple%20shapes%20and%20sizes%20in%20real%20rainy%20weather.%20Instead%2C%20I%20came%20up%20with%20a%20few%20tests%20to%20simulate%20rainy%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20verified%20the%20measurements%20of%20each%20by%20assessing%20their%20length%20from%20shoulder%20to%20tail%20and%20their%20girth%2C%20the%20width%20of%20the%20jacket%20at%20the%20chest's%20widest%20point.%20I%20took%20note%20of%20any%20jackets%20that%20differed%20from%20their%20advertised%20size%20or%20appeared%20to%20fit%20more%20tightly%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoak%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20soak%20test%20illustrated%20how%20each%20raincoat%20would%20stand%20up%20under%20heavy%20rain.%20Using%20leftover%20two-by-fours%2C%20we%20constructed%20a%20wooden%20dog%20with%20a%20belly%2013%20inches%20off%20the%20ground%20and%20a%20length%20of%2020%20inches.%20When%20Woody%20was%20ready%2C%20I%20wrapped%20a%20dry%20towel%20around%20its%20belly%20and%20dressed%20it%20in%20each%20jacket.%20I%20sprinkled%20the%20dog%20and%20raincoat%20with%20water%20from%20a%20hose%20for%20two%20minutes%2C%20then%20carefully%20removed%20the%20jacket%20to%20look%20for%20any%20spots%20where%20the%20water%20had%20seeped%20through.%20I%20also%20checked%20the%20interior%20lining%20of%20the%20jacket%20to%20see%20if%20moisture%20had%20penetrated%20without%20wetting%20the%20towel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleaning%20test%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20cleaning%20test%20had%20three%20parts.%20First%2C%20I%20wiped%20a%20handful%20of%20mud%20on%20the%20exterior%20of%20each%20jacket%20and%20let%20it%20dry%20overnight.%20Next%2C%20I%20attempted%20to%20wipe%20off%20the%20mud%20using%20a%20clean%2C%20dry%20cloth.%20Finally%2C%20I%20washed%20the%20raincoat%20according%20to%20the%20manufacturer's%20instructions%2C%20looking%20for%20any%20stains%20or%20other%20changes%20in%20the%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20fit%20your%20dog%20for%20a%20raincoat%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20fit%20your%20dog%20for%20a%20raincoat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDogs%20come%20in%20so%20many%20different%20shapes%20and%20sizes%20that%20fitting%20one%20for%20a%20raincoat%20can%20be%20a%20lengthy%20process%20of%20trial%20and%20error.%20Since%20there's%20no%20universal%20sizing%2C%20what%20one%20brand%20considers%20small%20could%20easily%20be%20considered%20large%20by%20a%20competitor.%20To%20get%20the%20right%20fit%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20grab%20a%20measuring%20tape%20and%20follow%20our%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELength%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20primary%20dimension%20used%20to%20determine%20the%20size%20of%20a%20raincoat%20is%20the%20length%20of%20a%20dog's%20back.%20Measure%20your%20dog%20from%20the%20top%20of%20their%20tail%20to%20their%20shoulder%20blades%20while%20they%20are%20standing%20in%20a%20relaxed%20position.%20If%20your%20measurement%20falls%20between%20sizes%2C%20size%20up.%20Some%20brands%20may%20recommend%20a%20specific%20size%20for%20certain%20breeds.%20This%20may%20be%20helpful%2C%20but%20don't%20follow%20their%20suggestions%20alone%2C%20as%20sizes%20can%20vary%20among%20a%20single%20breed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChest%20girth%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Dog%20raincoats%20are%20also%20commonly%20measured%20by%20chest%20girth.%20This%20is%20an%20important%20figure%20to%20get%20right%20because%20many%20jackets%20are%20not%20adjustable%20around%20the%20chest.%20That's%20doubly%20true%20if%20you%20have%20a%20broad-%20or%20barrel-chested%20pup.%20To%20get%20this%20figure%2C%20measure%20the%20circumference%20of%20your%20dog's%20chest%20while%20they%20are%20standing%20in%20a%20relaxed%20position%2C%20wrapping%20the%20tape%20right%20behind%20the%20legs%20at%20the%20chest's%20widest%20point.%20If%20your%20dog's%20chest%20girth%20falls%20between%20sizes%2C%20choose%20the%20larger%20option%2C%20especially%20if%20your%20dog%20does%20a%20lot%20of%20running%20and%20jumping.%20A%20highly%20active%20dog%20may%20benefit%20from%20a%20jacket%20that%20is%20an%20inch%20or%20two%20wider%20than%20their%20actual%20measurement%20because%20it%20will%20allow%20their%20front%20legs%20more%20freedom%20of%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENeck%20girth%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20make%20sure%20your%20jacket%20won't%20be%20too%20tight%20around%20the%20neck%2C%20measure%20around%20the%20thickest%20part%20right%20below%20the%20collar.%20This%20is%20particularly%20important%20if%20the%20coat's%20neck%20lacks%20an%20adjustable%20opening.%20When%20in%20doubt%2C%20size%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrop%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Occasionally%2C%20brands%20offer%20a%20drop%20measurement%20to%20help%20you%20get%20the%20right%20fit.%20The%20drop%20is%20how%20low%20a%20jacket%20hangs%20on%20a%20dog's%20body%20and%20legs.%20Too%20long%20and%20it%20may%20restrict%20movement%3B%20too%20short%2C%20and%20your%20pup%20may%20get%20wet%20by%20the%20end%20of%20a%20walk.%20Your%20dog's%20raincoat%20should%20extend%20at%20most%20halfway%20down%20the%20leg.%20To%20figure%20out%20how%20a%20jacket%20will%20lay%20on%20your%20dog%2C%20compare%20half%20its%20width%20to%20the%20distance%20between%20the%20top%20of%20your%20dog's%20tail%20to%20the%20ankle%20of%20their%20hind%20leg%20just%20above%20the%20paw.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20walk%20your%20dog%20in%20the%20rain%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20walk%20your%20dog%20in%20the%20rain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20dog%20hates%20leaving%20the%20house%20when%20the%20rain%20starts%20to%20fall%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20fitting%20them%20with%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20raincoats%2C%20these%20tips%20for%20wet-weather%20walking%20will%20make%20sure%20you%20get%20their%20most%20important%20daily%20needs%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20the%20right%20gear%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Make%20rainy%20day%20walks%20more%20enjoyable%20by%20getting%20your%20pup%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20raincoats.%20A%20properly%20fitted%20coat%20that%20covers%20both%20the%20chest%20and%20belly%20will%20prevent%20your%20dog%20from%20splashing%20water%20against%20the%20most%20sensitive%20parts%20of%20their%20body.%20If%20your%20dog%20has%20sensitive%20paws%2C%20you%20may%20also%20want%20to%20consider%20getting%20a%20set%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-boots%5C%22%3Ebest%20dog%20boots%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlan%20ahead%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Unless%20the%20forecast%20calls%20for%20extreme%20weather%2C%20most%20rainy%20days%20have%20at%20least%20a%20couple%20of%20periods%20in%20which%20showers%20slow%20to%20a%20sprinkle.%20Use%20a%20weather%20tracking%20app%20or%20website%20to%20help%20you%20predict%20when%20a%20storm%20will%20lighten%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEncourage%2C%20don't%20force%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20if%20you%20have%20the%20proper%20rain%20gear%20for%20your%20pup%2C%20your%20dog%20may%20still%20avoid%20the%20rain%20at%20all%20costs.%20These%20dogs%20will%20likely%20require%20an%20extra%20incentive.%20Before%20getting%20ready%20to%20go%2C%20stuff%20your%20pockets%20full%20of%20treats%20and%20offer%20them%20before%20you%20step%20out%20the%20door.%20If%20putting%20on%20rain%20gear%20predicts%20that%20treats%20will%20follow%2C%20your%20dog%20will%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20allow%20you%20to%20get%20them%20dressed.%20Use%20your%20treats%20to%20entice%20your%20dog%20out%20the%20door%20instead%20of%20forcing%20them%20to%20go%20out%20into%20the%20rain%2C%20which%20will%20only%20make%20them%20more%20frightened%20and%20stressed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlay%20the%20%26quot%3BFind%20It%26quot%3B%20game%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Keep%20the%20treats%20flowing%20once%20outside.%20Try%20encouraging%20your%20dog%20to%20walk%20with%20the%20Find%20It%20game.%20Throw%20a%20treat%20a%20few%20feet%20in%20front%20of%20your%20dog%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3Bfind%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20happy%20tone.%20Let%20them%20gobble%20up%20the%20treat%2C%20then%20throw%20your%20next%20one%2C%20repeating%20the%20phrase.%20Play%20the%20game%20as%20much%20as%20necessary%20during%20the%20walk%20to%20get%20your%20pup's%20mind%20off%20the%20water%20falling%20from%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20expect%20a%20regular%20walk%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20with%20plenty%20of%20treats%20and%20encouragement%2C%20dogs%20who%20really%20hate%20the%20rain%20aren't%20likely%20to%20want%20to%20stay%20outdoors%20for%20long.%20If%20they%20go%20potty%20and%20then%20refuse%20to%20go%20any%20farther%2C%20that's%20OK.%20Bring%20them%20back%20inside%20and%20make%20up%20the%20missed%20exercise%20with%20play%20or%20indoor%20training.%20Read%20more%20on%20backup%20plans%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStick%20to%20quiet%20streets%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20rainy%20days%2C%20when%20cars%20zoom%20through%20puddles%2C%20the%20busier%20the%20street%2C%20the%20louder%20it%20will%20be.%20And%20the%20more%20noise%2C%20the%20more%20frightened%20your%20dog%20is%20likely%20to%20feel%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%20mention%20all%20that%20potential%20for%20being%20splashed%20by%20passing%20vehicles.%20When