%2C%20dry%20cloth.%20Finally%2C%20I%20washed%20the%20raincoat%20according%20to%20the%20manufacturer's%20instructions%2C%20looking%20for%20any%20stains%20or%20other%20changes%20in%20the%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOther%20dog%20raincoats%20we%20tested%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20dog%20rain%20jackets%20that%20Insider%20tested%20are%20hanging%20on%20a%20fence.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F605e24f18e71b300185190ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20tested%20several%20jackets%20before%20selecting%20the%20best%20dog%20raincoats.%3Cp%3EShoshi%20Parks%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20else%20we%20recommend%20and%20why%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40833-20%26h%3Ddf268f94efcbe048b2a58958038d4bed75adf61169aca2fcee8ebbdb77305586%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f428fa%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-raincoat-for-dogs%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fgp%252Fproduct%252FB005SJDEBA%252Fref%253Das_li_tl%253Fie%253DUTF8%2526tag%253Dbiipgf_100319_best-raincoats-for-dogs-20%2526camp%253D1789%2526creative%253D9325%2526linkCode%253Das2%2526creativeASIN%253DB005SJDEBA%2526linkId%253Dd28f77c400a1cb3c18aeb51e935331f2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERC%20Pets%20Packable%20Rain%20Poncho%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Sydney%20Fontaine%2C%20a%20professional%20dog%20walker%2C%20trainer%2C%20and%20owner%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fzippypetcare.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZippy%20Pet%20Care%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20likes%20pairing%20this%20affordable%2C%20lightweight%20rain%20poncho%20with%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-sweaters%5C%22%3Ebes