20jacket%20made%20from%20recycled%20plastic%20bottles%20provides%20excellent%20coverage%20of%20the%20chest%2C%20belly%2C%20and%20front%20legs%20and%20comes%20in%2010%20sizes%20with%20several%20points%20of%20adjustment.%20Its%20design%2C%20which%20includes%20leg%20holes%20and%20a%20long%20zipper%20down%20the%20side%2C%20made%20it%20a%20major%20challenge%20to%20get%20on%20and%20off.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-40833-20%26h%3D030361ad79c3eb05148b7c8d10ada4cca9628eaff292aa34117ae216ea99466b%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f428fa%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-raincoat-for-dogs%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fgp%252Fproduct%252FB07RTZ7DL4%252Fref%253Das_li_tl%253Fie%253DUTF8%2526tag%253Dbiipgf_100319_best-raincoats-for-dogs-20%2526camp%253D1789%2526creative%253D9325%2526linkCode%253Das2%2526creativeASIN%253DB07RTZ7DL4%2526linkId%253Dea6d5a13c7d4d371222b14cbbcb09856%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurgo%20Portsmouth%20Foul%20Weather%20Rain%20Jacket%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20I%20liked%20the%20design%20of%20this%20rain%20jacket%20which%2C%20like%20Ruffwear's%20Sun%20Shower%2C%20is%20a%20vest%20style%20with%20buckles%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20belly.%20But%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20testing%20period%2C%20this%20jacket%20had%20gone%20from%20looking%20brand%20new%20to%20shabby.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20to%20fit%20your%20dog%20for%20a%20raincoat%3Cp%3EDogs%20come%20in%20so%20many%20different%20shapes%20and%20sizes%20that%20fitting%20one%20for%20a%20raincoat%20can%20be%20a%20lengthy%20process%20of%20trial%20and%20error.%20Since%20there's%20no%20universal%20sizing%2C%20what%20one%20brand%20considers%20small%20could%20easily%20be%20considered%20large%20by%20a%20competitor.%20To%20get%20the%20right%20fit%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20grab%20a%20measuring%20tape%20and%20follow%20our%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELength%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20primary%20dimension%20used%20to%20determine%20the%20size%20of%20a%20raincoat%20is%20the%20length%20of%20a%20dog's%20back.%20Measure%20your%20dog%20from%20the%20top%20of%20their%20tail%20to%20their%20shoulder%20blades%20while%20they%20are%20standing%20in%20a%20relaxed%20position.%20If%20your%20measurement%20falls%20between%20sizes%2C%20size%20up.%20Some%20brands%20may%20recommend%20a%20specific%20size%20for%20certain%20breeds.%20This%20may%20be%20helpful%2C%20but%20don't%20follow%20their%20suggestions%20alone%2C%20as%20sizes%20can%20vary%20among%20a%20single%20breed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChest%20girth%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Dog%20raincoats%20are%20also%20commonly%20measured%20by%20chest%20girth.%20This%20is%20an%20important%20figure%20to%20get%20right%20because%20many%20jackets%20are%20not%20adjustable%20around%20the%20chest.%20That's%20doubly%20true%20if%20you%20have%20a%20broad-%20or%20barrel-chested%20pup.%20To%20get%20this%20figure%2C%20measure%20the%20circumference%20of%20your%20dog's%20chest%20while%20they%20are%20standing%20in%20a%20relaxed%20position%2C%20wrapping%20the%20tape%20right%20behind%20the%20legs%20at%20the%20chest's%20widest%20point.%20If%20your%20dog's%20chest%20girth%20falls%20between%20sizes%2C%20choose%20the%20larger%20option%2C%20especially%20if%20your%20dog%20does%20a%20lot%20of%20running%20and%20jumping.%20A%20highly%20active%20dog%20may%20benefit%20from%20a%20jacket%20that%20is%20an%20inch%20or%20two%20wider%20than%20their%20actual%20measurement%20because%20it%20will%20allow%20their%20front%20legs%20more%20freedom%20of%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENeck%20girth%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20make%20sure%20your%20jacket%20won't%20be%20too%20tight%20around%20the%20neck%2C%20measure%20around%20the%20thickest%20part%20right%20below%20the%20collar.%20This%20is%20particularly%20important%20if%20the%20coat's%20neck%20lacks%20an%20adjustable%20opening.%20When%20in%20doubt%2C%20size%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrop%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Occasionally%2C%20brands%20offer%20a%20drop%20measurement%20to%20help%20you%20get%20the%20right%20fit.%20The%20drop%20is%20how%20low%20a%20jacket%20hangs%20on%20a%20dog's%20body%20and%20legs.%20Too%20long%20and%20it%20may%20restrict%20movement%3B%20too%20short%2C%20and%20your%20pup%20may%20get%20wet%20by%20the%20end%20of%20a%20walk.%20Your%20dog's%20raincoat%20should%20extend%20at%20most%20halfway%20down%20the%20leg.%20To%20figure%20out%20how%20a%20jacket%20will%20lay%20on%20your%20dog%2C%20compare%20half%20its%20width%20to%20the%20distance%20between%20the%20top%20of%20your%20dog's%20tail%20to%20the%20ankle%20of%20their%20hind%20leg%20just%20above%20the%20paw.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20do%20you%20walk%20your%20dog%20on%20a%20rainy%20day%3F%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20dog%20hates%20leaving%20the%20house%20when%20the%20rain%20starts%20to%20fall%2C%20these%20tips%20for%20wet-weather%20walking%20will%20make%20sure%20you%20get%20their%20most%20important%20daily%20needs%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20the%20right%20gear%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Make%20rainy%20day%20walks%20more%20enjoyable%20by%20getting%20your%20pup%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20raincoats.%20A%20properly%20fitted%20coat%20that%20covers%20both%20the%20chest%20and%20belly%20will%20prevent%20your%20dog%20from%20splashing%20water%20against%20the%20most%20sensitive%20parts%20of%20their%20body.%20If%20your%20dog%20has%20sensitive%20paws%2C%20you%20may%20also%20want%20to%20consider%20getting%20a%20set%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-boots%5C%22%3Ebest%20dog%20boots%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlan%20ahead%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Unless%20the%20forecast%20calls%20for%20extreme%20weather%2C%20most%20rainy%20days%20have%20at%20least%20a%20couple%20of%20periods%20in%20which%20showers%20slow%20to%20a%20sprinkle.%20Use%20a%20weather%20tracking%20app%20or%20