ect.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwho-are-the-reichsbuergers-far-right-plotters-who-tried-to-overthrow-german-government-standing-trial-13125613%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwho-are-the-reichsbuergers-far-right-plotters-who-tried-to-overthrow-german-government-standing-trial-13125613%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Engineers%20Raise%20Rs%201%20Cr%20in%20Funding%20For%20Innovative%20%E2%80%98Socks%E2%80%99%20That%20Have%20Saved%2020%2C000%20Newborn%20Lives%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESupriya%20(name%20changed)%20gave%20birth%20to%20her%20baby%20girl%20at%2032%20weeks%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Her%20husband%20is%20an%20electrician%20while%20she%20works%20as%20a%20contract%20labourer.%20Her%20baby%20was%20born%20in%20a%20local%20hospital%20which%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20provide%20the%20adequate%20care%20required%20to%20monitor%20and%20safeguard%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20baby%20had%20hypothermia%20for%20the%20first%20few%20weeks%20of%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20suggested%20that%20the%20couple%20take%20the%20baby%20to%20the%20closest%20district%20government%20hospital%20for%20better%20care%20and%20attention.%20The%20nearest%20hospital%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F249309%2Flow-cost-innovation-caremother-baby-heartbeat-marico-mumbai-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpecial%20Newborn%20Care%20Unit%20(SNCU)%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20three%20hours%20away%2C%20and%20the%20baby%20would%20have%20to%20be%20transported%20in%20an%20ambulance.%20The%20couple%20borrowed%20money%20from%20family%20and%20friends%20as%20they%20were%20determined%20to%20provide%20the%20best%20care%20possible%20for%20their%20precious%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20staying%20in%20an%20incubator%20for%20almost%2045%20days%2C%20their%20baby%20girl%2C%20Kavya%2C%20is%20a%20thriving%20toddler%20today.%20This%2C%20howev