0His%20day%20begins%20with%20going%20into%20the%20forest%20and%20chopping%20wood%2C%20followed%20by%20working%20in%20a%20stone%20quarry%20towards%20the%20afternoon.%20In%20the%20evening%2C%20Shyambabu%20sells%20the%20wood%20that%20he%20has%20cut%2C%20earning%20a%20meagre%20Rs%20100%20on%20a%20good%20day%20and%20Rs%2080%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20years%2C%20Shyambabu%20has%20remained%20unfazed%20by%20adversity.%20Years%20ago%20he%20devised%20a%20hack%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20thorny%20shrubs%20and%20stones%20that%20lay%20along%20his%20path%20into%20the%20forest.%20%E2%80%9CI%20make%20a%20bandage%20out%20of%20leaves%20and%20rope%2C%20and%20wear%20it%20on%20my%20feet%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20helps%20me%20walk%20through%20the%20forest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FDonate-A-Slipper%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonate%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FDonate-A-Slipper%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347562%2Fcoolant-device-delhi-architect-innovates-eco-friendly-affordable-cooler-to-reduce-power-bills-watch%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20innovation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20ingenious%20as%20it%20may%20be%2C%20is%20a%20temporary%20shield.%20By%20midday%2C%20a%20burning%20sensation%20beneath%20his%20feet%20alerts%20Shyambabu%20that%20his%20%E2%80%98self-made%20slipper%E2%80%99%20has%20fallen%20off.%20He%20must%20now%20endure%20the%20unforgiving%20hot%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20years%2C%20his%20feet%20have%20developed%20calluses%20and%20corns%2C%20and%20turned%20black.%20One%20might%20wonder%20why%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20purchase%20a%20pai