5085%2Feco-tourism-helps-rural-woman-earn-mangroves-of-sindhudurg-rashmi-sawant-homestays-konkan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplatform%20that%20facilitated%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20through%20education%2C%20women%20empowerment%2C%20health%2C%20and%20sanitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20today%2C%20it%20is%20a%20movement%20with%20students%20from%20universities%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20Kashi%20Vidyapeeth%2C%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%20(BHU)%2C%20and%20Delhi%20University%20(DU)%20%E2%80%94%20leading%20change%20from%20the%20front.%20This%20summer%2C%20Divyanshu%20and%20his%20team%20are%20attempting%20to%20bring%20respite%20to%20the%20daily%20wage%20labourers%20of%20Mirzapur%20and%20Sonbhadra%20through%20their%20slipper%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%20And%20Divyanshu%20needs%20your%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBring%20hope%20to%20someone%20with%20just%20Rs%20100%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20were%20given%20a%20pair%20of%20slippers%2C%20would%20that%20help%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20question%20is%20directed%20towards%20Vikas%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20labourer%20who%20works%20at%20the%20stone%20casting%20site%20along%20with%20Shyambabu.%20He%20pauses%20before%20answering%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20make%20me%20very%20happy.%20Thorns%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20hurt%20my%20feet%20anymore%20and%20the%20burning%20would%20stop.%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20walk%20without%20getting%20scared%20that%20stones%20will%20pierce%20my%20feet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20heartbreaking%20to%20hear%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F255924%2Fmyvacc-bengaluru-startup-covid-19-free-vaccination-mumbai-pune-unorganised-sector-daily-wagers-slum-dwellers-domestic-help-coronavirus-covid-19-pandemic-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethese%20labourers%E2%80%9