2%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Family%20Made%20Their%20Cement-Free%20Dream%20Home%20Using%20Neem%20%26amp%3B%20Jaggery%20as%20Building%20Material%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20heatwave%20is%20sweeping%20through%20the%20country%20with%20temperatures%20crossing%2040%20degrees%20Celcius%20in%20many%20cities%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291472%2Fuk-london-europe-heatwave-how-to-stay-cool-traditional-indian-hacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforcing%20us%20to%20use%20air%20conditioners%20at%20all%20times%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20the%20climate%20gets%20more%20extreme%2C%20we%20all%20dream%20of%20living%20in%20a%20home%20that%20could%20adapt%20to%20different%20weather%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20way%20homes%20were%20constructed%20earlier%2C%20before%20cement%20became%20a%20necessity%20for%20construction.%20Shipra%20Singhania%20has%20built%20such%20a%20dreamy%20sustainable%20home%20in%20Alwar%2C%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20architect%20runs%20Sketch%20Design%20Studio%2C%20and%20built%20this%202%2C000%20square%20feet%20home%20using%20natural%20materials%C2%A0%20and%20revived%20ancient%20techniques.%20The%20home%20is%20built%20using%20mud%20and%20earth%20sacks%20along%20with%20lime%20and%20plaster.%20She%20even%20incorporated%20neem%20leaves%2C%20turmeric%20and%20jaggery%20in%20the%20building%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20edibles%20have%20been%20used%20for%20years%20in%20earthen%20constructions%20due%20to%20their%20many%20properties%20%E2%80%94%20neem%20keeps%20termites%20at%20bay%2C%20while%20jaggery%20is%20a%20great%20binding%20material%2C%20and%20methi%20(fenugreek)%2C%20too%2C%20binds%20the%20bricks%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shipra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20challenge%20was%20designing%20for%20Alwar%E2%80%99s%20extreme%20climate%2C%20with%20temperatures%20going%20from%20as%20high%20as%2041%20degrees%20Celcius%20to%20as%20low%20as%208%20degrees%20Celcius%20in%20the%20winters.%20The%20architect%20designed%20the%20home%20in%20a%20strategic%20manner%20to%20maintain%20a%20comfortable%20climate%20inside%20all%20year-round.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20%E2%80%93%20it%20has%20zero%20cement.%20The%20central%20roof%20at%20a%20height%20of%2023%20feet%2C%20along%20with%20huge%20windsor%2C%20ensures%20proper%20ventilation%20and%20sunlight%20penetration.%C2%A0%20Adding%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335976%2Fmumbai-sustainable-home-ecofriendly-mud-architecture-geeli-mitti-ngo-lakhichand-jain%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estructural%20sustainability%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20the%20rainwater%20harvesting%20and%20greywater%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%20about%20the%20house%20here%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FHmzFuD6ZfhQ%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FHmzFuD6ZfhQ%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714051782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FHmzFuD6ZfhQ%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348313%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shipra%20Singhania%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Alwar%2C%20Rajasthan%20is%20built%20using%20natural%2C%20cooling%20materials%20like%20neem%2C%20jaggery%2C%20and%20turmeric.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348313%2Falwar-zero-cement-sustainable-home-rainwater-harvesting-neem-jaggery-built-by-shipra-singhania%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Once%20Featured%20in%20%E2%80%98Life%20of%20Pi%E2%80%99%2C%20This%20Puducherry%20Homestay%20is%20a%20200-YO%20Heritage%20Villa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20morning%20last%20year%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20Puducherry%20was%20fast%20asleep%2C%20Sudeep%20Sen%2C%20a%20Bengali%20poet%2C%20was%20working%20on%20a%20new%20piece.%20The%20protagonist%20was%20an%20iron%20safe%20embedded%20in%20a%20wall%20of%20his%20room%20at%20the%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20homestay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Room%204%2C%20the%20safe%20in%20the%20wall%20has%20not%20been%20opened%20in%20a%20150%20years%E2%80%A6It%20has%20seen%20history%2C%20life%20changing%2C%20aging%20%E2%80%94%20but%20no%20one%20knows%20what%20lies%20within.%20But%20what%20is%20inside%3F%20%E2%80%94%20The%20first%20owner%E2%80%99s%20ashes%2C%20her%20will%2C%20wealth%2C%20gold%3B%20old%20currencies%2C%20lover%E2%80%99s%20relics%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20stanzas%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20does%20make%20for%20a%20very%20compelling%20read%2C%20Siddarth%20Saikia%2C%20the%20owner%20and%20manager%20of%20affairs%20at%20the%20homestay%2C%20says%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20piece%20of%20fiction%3B%20the%20safe%20exists.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20key%20is%20lost%20in%20time%2C%20and%20the%20safe%E2%80%99s%20outer%20frame%20bears%20many%20markings.%20Many%20have%20tried%20to%20prise%20it%20open%20to%20check%20what%20it%20contains%2C%20but%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20budge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20a%20professional%20locksmith%2C%20who%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20through%2C%20informed%20Siddarth%20and%20the%20family%20that%20the%20safe%E2%80%99s%20rusted%20interiors%20and%20strategic%20position%20within%20the%20wall%20meant%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20crack%20it%20open%20would%20be%20to%20break%20down%20the%20wall%20itself.%20And%20no%20one%20wanted%20to%20resort%20to%20this%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20to%20this%20day%2C%20the%20safe%20lies%20untouched%20by%20the%20fingers%20of%20time%2C%20holding%20within%20it%20many%20mysteries%20and%20adding%20its%20own%20little%20bit%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344999%2Fhomestay-in-panchgani-roadtrip-from-mumbai-sustainable-organic-food-solar-panel-long-weekend-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintrigue%20to%20the%20property%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20attractive%20as%20it%20is%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20draw%20at%20the%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20homestay%20helmed%20by%20a%20mother-son%20duo%20from%20Delhi.%20The%20vibrant%20yellows%20of%20the%20bungalow%20are%20a%20sight%20for%20sore%20eyes%2C%20its%20layout%20offering%20pockets%20of%20unexpected%20calm%20to%20the%20weary%20traveller%20or%20to%20anyone%20who%20comes%20looking%20for%20some%20peace%20and%20quiet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWould%20you%20believe%20it%20if%20you%20were%20told%20that%20not%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20this%20sprawling%20paradise%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccrumbling%20and%20dilapidated%20spot%E2%80%9D%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%2C%20and%20so%2C%20Siddarth%20settled%20down%20for%20a%20tete-a-tete%20with%