ge-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-2048x1536.jpeg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348060%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBharat%20and%20Shaaswat%20swam%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20India%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaaswat%20Sharma%20(31)%2C%20a%20technical%20architect%2C%20is%20an%20ultra%20long-distance%20swimmer%2C%20triathlete%2C%20national%20water%20polo%20player%2C%20and%20swimmer.%20He%20holds%20all%20India%20records%20and%20over%20500%20medals%20and%20trophies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20athletes%20started%20their%20foray%20into%20athletics%20at%20the%20school%20itself%20and%20participated%20in%20national%20and%20international%20competitions.%20After%20swimming%20in%20events%20around%20the%20world%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20embark%20on%20what%20they%20call%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20toughest%20stretches%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20think%20of%20a%20tough%20swim%2C%20everyone%20always%20mentions%20places%20around%20the%20world%2C%20while%20forgetting%20that%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20stretch%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20difficult.%20Only%20a%20few%20have%20attempted%20and%20completed%20it%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20put%20it%20on%20the%20global%20map%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20idea%20in%20mind%2C%20and%20to%20foster%20positive%20relationships%20between%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20they%20started%20preparations%20in%20earnest%20almost%20three%20years%20back%2C%20says%20the%20swimmer.%20They%20christened%20the%20expedition%20the%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Setu%20Swimming%20Expedition%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20started%20planning%20and%20practising%20for%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20prepared%20in%20different%20water%20and%20weather%20conditions%20with%20an%20experienced%20crew%20guiding%20them%2C%20and%20training%20them%20on%20water%20safety%20and%20preventing%20accidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20their%20practice%20was%20indoors%2C%20swimming%20in%20the%20open%20waters%20was%20a%20completely%20different%20ballgame%2C%20concedes%20Bharat%2C%20which%20accentuates%20the%20need%20for%20better%20infrastructure%20and%20investment%20to%20promote%20such%20sports%20in%20the%20country.%20He%20adds%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286757%2Fpara-swimmer-spina-bifida-breaks-asian-record-niranjan-mukundan-surgeries-medals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen-water%20swimming%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20a%20very%20popular%20sport%20in%20India%2C%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20promoted.%20And%20to%20also%20bring%20this%20to%20the%20public%20eye%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20set%20an%20example%20by%20accomplishing%20this%20incredible%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20efforts%20will%20be%20successful%20when%20we%20see%20more%20young%20talent%20from%20India%20opting%20for%20swimming%20and%20representing%20the%20country%20at%20prestigious%20national%20and%20international%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20undertake%20this%20initiative%2C%20the%20swimmers%20received%20permissions%20from%20relevant%20authorities%20like%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20India%20(MEA)%3B%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20India%20(MoD)%3B%20Ministry%20of%20Health%2C%20India%20(MoHFW)%3B%20High%20Commission%20of%20India%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%3B%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%3B%20and%20other%20Government%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETesting%20your%20mental%20and%20physical%20fitness%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20preparing%20and%20getting%20the%20necessary%20permissions%20from%20the%20two%20Governments%2C%20the%20Navy%20and%20the%20Coast%20Guard%2C%20th